list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add new project configuration files
The commit introduces several new configuration files for our project. These files include Local_Grader.iml, which configures a new Python module, modules.xml, which defines the project's module, inspectionProfiles/profiles_settings.xml that sets up project's profile settings, vcs.xml for specifying VCS settings, and .gitignore to exclude certain files from the repository.
